nodes.text: General Orma Hundeen along with Zeela Nall, Nuri Pravada, Sheyne Tyndos and Leia Organa were on a mission on Elerion to recover the holocube map containing the location of Rebel main bases from Nescan Tal'yo, Hermos and Gogol.
Although appearing to be Human, her eyes had cat-like irises and were completely green-yellow.
